article_id:1085,category_name:Events,title_name:Ebon Chimera Will Debut in Void Battles!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/ae98c6183f1cb78f7c8da1ed82f96c5d.png,message:<div>Ebon Chimera will appear in Void Battles starting <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1582178400"></span>.</div><div>Weapons you can craft using materials obtained from the Ebon Chimera will also be added.</div><div><br></div><div>A chimera possessed by an insatiable loathing has absorbed black mana, lending even greater power to the flames of hatred that char its body. Its maddening breath sucks the light from the living, leaving them a husk of their former selves that will eventually succumb to their own malice.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/42f216ee2ec87a33b06c1dec90eb9392.png"></div><div>Ebon Chimera (Shadow), Required Might: 13,000</div><div><br></div><div>■New Weapons You Can Craft Using Materials Obtained From the Ebon Chimera</div><div>Powerful new weapons will be added to the Void weapon series lineup under Crafting starting <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1582178400"></span>.</div><div>You must have first obtained specific weapons before you can craft weapons using materials obtained from Ebon Chimera.</div><div>The required weapons are the shadow-attuned 5★ weapons which can be crafted using materials obtained from the Proud Manticore.</div><div><br></div><div>The weapon that is required differs based on the weapon type for the weapon you wish to craft. You can check the requirements by selecting Materials for the Ebon Chimera weapons on the Craft tab under Crafting.</div><div>Note: Weapons crafted using materials obtained from the Ebon Chimera cannot be dismantled.</div><div><br></div><div>Note:</div><div>Players must have completed up to Chapter 7 / 5-6 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate in Void Battles.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost!</div><div><br></div>,start_time:1582005600,update_time1581672218